Jacket. Jacket. Jacket.

01:11.114 --> 01:13.116
- Okay, see you later.

01:13.116 --> 01:15.684
♪ For every Johnny
that wants a car ♪

01:15.684 --> 01:19.905
♪ Every junior
that wants a mobile bike ♪

01:19.905 --> 01:22.212
♪ That rides
