Flaxman's Auction House.

01:35.573 --> 01:37.227
How may I direct your call?

01:37.227 --> 01:39.882
♪ Just to lean her head
in their arms ♪

01:41.579 --> 01:45.192
♪ What a Christmas present,
this Christmas ♪

01:45.192 --> 01:48.630
♪ Oh, what a gift you could be

01:48.630 --> 01:51.415
♪ You know if I could
just give out ♪

01:51.415 --> 01:53.591
♪ Christmas presents
to everyone ♪

01:53.591 --> 01:55.637
♪ Under one great big
